}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== OEM Gemtek WADI-125GN (WADI-125GN_V01A)
"WADI-125GN_V00" and "ENG-X10-0300R RoHS" is silkscreened :on the board in the initial FCC filing made 09/10/2008. :The RAM chip in these photos is a 32MB '''Nanya''' NT5DS16M16CS-5T. :The Switch is an [[IC+]] IP175E. "WADI-125GN_V01A" and "190-c05-7101R RoHS" is silkscreened :on the board in the C2PC made 10/08/2008. :The RAM chip in the new photos is a 32MB '''Qimonda''' HYB25DC256160CE-5.
Default settings are from the FCC manual. :The default SSID pattern ''may'' be '''Belkin_N_ADSL_XXXXXX'''.
